nodes.bodyText: I believe the name of this file is generated by snowpack, right? That means this "link" is not valid. And I presume there's no way to make it constant, correct? If that's the case I guess it's ok (automatically updating the file name here per each dist build would be a significant overhead). But if it's possible to use a static name for this file, we should do it so that the license files would point to a valid file.
